建造技术非常特别。

62
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,560
That's right.
没错。

63
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:11,200
And sometimes you might hear us talk about the Great Wall instead of the Great Wall of
有时候你可能会听到我们只说“长城”，而不是“中国的长城”。

64
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,440
China.


65
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:14,480
