Well yeah, you're taking value back, right?
嗯，是的，你在找回价值，对吧？

160
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:46,320
And so in the case of Jesus, he is taking away the sins of the world and he's redeeming,
所以在耶稣的情况下，他带走世人的罪过，进行救赎。

161
